{"tid":2122001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"慈雲山捐血人士確診    紅血球已輸給瑪嘉烈一名病人需檢測","createTime":"2020-07-23T16:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T17:21:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ad01841fb84070112bc22050065fe092db554f34","tid":2122001,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T16:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RUTQcrtovUg0ATbBLkhZUw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200723a170933.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRUTQcrtovUg0ATbBLkhZUw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200723a170933.jpg&h=3da08c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/慈雲山捐血人士確診-紅血球已輸給瑪嘉烈-名病人需檢測-090500710.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%85%88%E9%9B%B2%E5%B1%B1%E6%8D%90%E8%A1%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%B4%85%E8%A1%80%E7%90%83%E5%B7%B2%E8%BC%B8%E7%B5%A6%E7%91%AA%E5%98%89%E7%83%88-%E5%90%8D%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%80%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-090500710.html&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6K3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=d31f3719\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/慈雲山捐血人士確診-紅血球已輸給瑪嘉烈-名病人需檢測-090500710.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】醫管局公布，紅十字會輸血服務中心發現，昨日一名捐血人士確診新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n輸血中心追查發現，7月9日患者在慈雲山中心流動捐血隊，曾經捐血。其紅血球已經輸給瑪嘉烈醫院一名病人，會跟進病人及安排進行新型冠狀病毒測試。<br />\n<br />\n確診者的血漿者未用已經回收。捐血人士在東區醫院留醫，情況穩定，家人也確診，相信與捐血無關。抽血職員有合適的防護裝備感染風險不高。"},{"pid":"6c5650fbcc2296dc52321715085e82cf49c1851a","tid":2122001,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"藍十字會仲不停叫人捐血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫popo 捐啦"},{"pid":"ae8b3949383c3d283f5a4c1be1762cf709d6f7d5","tid":2122001,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"叫差佬捐呀嘛 屌你老母"},{"pid":"f45e73a4948a658f67c66a846cd7cfa803efaf57","tid":2122001,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54ecd5b97a24f808ef14bfa1fdc533a4cf14786","tid":2122001,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae8b3949383c3d283f5a4c1be1762cf709d6f7d5","tid":2122001,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"叫差佬捐呀嘛 屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"有aids<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}